BT 1 0 0 1 0 99 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (The immune system is a coherence maintenance apparatus. Its fundamental task -- distinguishing self from non-self -- is a) Tj T* (measurement problem. The immune system measures whether incoming antigens match the body's "pointer states") Tj T* (\(self-antigens, established via thymic selection = einselection, Paper 02\). When gamma_eff of the immune system itself) Tj T* (remains below gamma_c, the distinction is reliable \(healthy immunity\). When gamma_eff rises \(from chronic inflammation,) Tj T* (toxins, or systemic stress\), the immune system loses discriminative power. At gamma_eff = gamma_c, self/non-self) Tj T* (discrimination collapses -) Tj (> autoimmunity. The cytokine storm \(COVID-19, sepsis\) is the immunological wind-up: gamma_eff) Tj T* (spikes catastrophically, the entire immune discrimination system passes gamma_c simultaneously, and the system cannot) Tj T* (down-regulate. Every inflammatory marker \(IL-6, CRP, TNF-alpha\) is a gamma_eff measurement. NIR-mediated reduction) Tj T* (of inflammatory markers \(Bootstrap Loop, Paper 02\) is the immunological analog of reducing gamma_eff below gamma_c.) Tj T* ET
